# Vercel deploy after `git push`

Read the full checklist in **`docs/VERCEL-GIT-DEPLOY.md`** (single source of truth: isolation steps, dashboard URLs, copy-paste prompt).

Summary: if `git ls-remote` shows the new SHA but Vercel does not build, run **`npx vercel deploy --prod`**. If that works, reconnect Git in Vercel and verify GitHub webhook deliveries; if it fails, fix the build first.
